e><br />\n食過心齊橋果間 冇咩特別 份量又少<br />\n去D 本地人開既餐廳可能仲有心做過佢"},{"pid":"f6b8c070a270d912a966f8658ebc4ea84459aca3","tid":296892,"uid":15302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:21:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係日本狗都唔屌<br />\n出咗國變寶物<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大阪果間中午至夜晚都要排隊 有本地人排 不過真係好食過香港果間好多<br />\n<br />\n香港果間之前聽人講話同日本果啲差唔多 但我食過tst果間兩次唔好食</blockquote><br />\n食過心齊橋果間 冇咩特別 份量又少<br />\n去D 本地人開既餐廳可能仲有心做過佢</blockquote><br />\n如果真係狗都唔屌 邊有錢出國開分店呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但本地黎講一定唔會係最好食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96c02ef5cdbe0be79d7135dd2919fc32868f00b","tid":296892,"uid":6268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:22:33.000Z","msg":"唔好話香港台灣要排<br />\n上次去京都想食宵夜<br />\n排九左成個鐘呀屌"},{"pid":"3b16da479af339134cccb0cbf17a53576973283e","tid":296892,"uid":63001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:24:00.000Z","msg":"係日本食從來唔洗排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dcd8afa25d7476e062c3f3adf5980fdc3a99719","tid":296892,"uid":4308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:25:57.000Z","msg":"拉麵冇咩特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻溫泉蛋好食"},{"pid":"a59ee889b6b54139b128c98a3fd3959d48a9190d","tid":296892,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:27:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係日本食從來唔洗排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日本食禁機出飛-&gt;等食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c09ab289e20d9ab6539382e1090d5709224cd0","tid":296892,"uid":118413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:30:55.000Z","msg":"我係本通果到 無人食既