edBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:49:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔好話香港台灣要排<br />\n上次去京都想食宵夜<br />\n排九左成個鐘呀屌</blockquote><br />\n點解你會排</blockquote><br />\n日本打工仔好夜放工，又無乜鋪開通宵。宵夜一蘭間唔中好多人。<br />\n<br />\nbtw 見到人多，去7-11 買飯糰好過"},{"pid":"39f6046cba209b36894d5ffcfda1dfa87aee3105","tid":296892,"uid":92021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:50:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一蘭有日本仔食 = 譚仔有香港人食<br />\n但你唔會話譚仔好食囉<br />\n<br />\n有日本人食同好唔好食係有分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊有日本人食一蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪玩啦 有當地人食一蘭架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常都係 上班族 一個人食<br />\n冇乜 後生仔 會去食</blockquote><br />\n人冇香港同台灣咁多<br />\n但絕對唔係冇人去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會冇人食因為大把遊客去食"},{"pid":"fe74857b9e657bbfdd5a788cbd1aba56f16a70bf","tid":296892,"uid":5804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:51:45.000Z","msg":"一蘭真係狗也不屌<br />\n利申 staff"},{"pid":"fbc9d2593d5185f408ca3de128c5302f6ba6d92a","tid":296892,"uid":50041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:52:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>台灣人比香港人更鍾意排隊<br />\n<img src=\"https://image1.thenewslens.com/2015/09/1384388_415877258523906_23222485_n-1.jpg?q=100&amp;w=1080\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage1.thenewslens.com%2F2015%2F09%2F1384388_415877258523906_23222485_n-1.jpg%3Fq%3D100%26w%3D1080&h=71eae3f4&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港人咪一撚樣<br />\n台灣人奶香港 以為香港好好真係得啖笑</blockquote><br />\n睇你個名就知你群開班友底質je<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一有咖啡雪糕買一送一優惠都大撚把人排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae4439974cb998b226df1ee1f934dfe37950a277","tid":296892,"uid":92021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:53:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一蘭真係狗也不屌<br />\n利申 staff</blockquote><br />\n前員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9890956ae9cf976e15ef9aeafdda147b08481ca7","tid":296892,"uid":392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:54:16.000Z","msg":"下次不如吹奏金龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c41ffa9c00da7a30c7c57f6f99a3b2bce0094f","tid":296892,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:56:44.000Z","msg":"上星期去大板，HEP FIVE附近有間關東煮好多人排隊，大部分日本人，我地又一齊排。 其實間野食物正自然有人排，好正常。 不過連登高登一向對排隊反感。"},{"pid":"e67fc8db3d1a029f298b1c2dae12b29a8bc4e19e","tid":296892,"uid":5804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:57:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一蘭真係狗也不屌<br />\n利申 staff</blockquote><br />\n前員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nKai 打嘛 Hi sand啦<br />\n利申叉燒仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc96ae8ef0673972c139eb9ef9f650cc43bbcfd4","tid":296892,"uid":35653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:58:24.000Z","msg":"50步笑100步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a09a17fc83bf680c910b18d2404fb7f6a6bc42c","tid":296892,"uid":10035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:59:04.000Z","msg":"屌 我排過心齋橋果間 ，覺得好撚好食，果點紅色辣辣地真係點精"},{"pid":"b8f9111b7a6fbd0be03b5134e1764a2db61ca11b","tid":296892,"uid":41744,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:59:30.000Z","msg":"成撚日見到堆人話冇日本人會食<br />\n狗都唔屌<br />\n屌你明明個陣係大阪睇日本節目<br />\n唔知乜柒最受歡迎拉麵第二<br />\n